<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11126</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19326</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“呃！外面好冷！” 奥利维亚边说边走进了厨房，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19326</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21359</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“准备好去滑冰了吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21359</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你猜猜谁不跟我们一起去？” 凯蒂皱着眉头说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28991</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奥利维亚看着双胞胎。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28991</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31613</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“乔伊？为什么不去呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31613</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35929</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我终于选好了我的领袖，所以我得做我的作业。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35929</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39577</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>还有两天就要发表了！” 乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39577</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43653</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奥利维亚点了点头，“我理解。” 她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46935</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你理解？” 凯蒂问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46935</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51627</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯。你需要我们帮你吗？” 奥利维亚问乔伊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51627</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55014</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们？” 凯蒂重复道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55014</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59533</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊没理凯蒂的话，对着朋友露出了微笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59533</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我自己能完成的。不过，你们可以帮我解开鸡圈的谜团。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69845</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊认为如果是哈丽特·塔布曼的话，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69845</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73346</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一定不会对需要帮助的鸡置之不理的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73346</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76299</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“算我一个。” 奥利维亚说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76299</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81986</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别算我，” 凯蒂说，“那些母鸡不是我的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81986</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85973</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们三个，想喝点热可可吗？” 妈妈问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85973</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91040</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“想，谢谢！” 三个女孩儿一起回答说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91040</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96911</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奥利维亚看向凯蒂，“贝柔老师告诉我们，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96911</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99829</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们得像我们的领袖一样行动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99829</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102587</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当亚伯拉罕·林肯的朋友......</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102587</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106856</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不！他的姐姐需要帮助时， 他会去滑冰吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106856</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111996</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂叹了口气，“应该不会的。” 她承认说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111996</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“乔伊，你需要我们做什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122480</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个小时后，女孩儿们来到了鸡圈，乔伊又数了一遍鸡。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122480</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127587</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，不！” 她大吃一惊，“现在丢了四只！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127587</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133478</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊想要哭，可她知道，一个领袖得有责任感。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133478</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137124</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“需要一个人去找它们，” 她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137124</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141226</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“另一个人得弄清楚它们是怎么逃出去的，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141226</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146725</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>还有一个人得在这儿看着这两只，以防它们也跑了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146725</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150014</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我去找母鸡。” 奥利维亚提议说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150014</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154079</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我去查鸡圈是否有漏洞。” 凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154079</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157400</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好极了，我们开始行动吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157400</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164127</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊砸碎了小水盆里的冰，然后把母鸡的食槽也填满了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164127</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170564</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>几分钟后，奥利维亚喊道：“嘿！在这儿！我发现了什么。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170564</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173748</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她在树屋下挥着手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173748</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176795</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>双胞胎跑了过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176795</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182928</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奥利维亚站在一堆落叶和干草旁边，那是爷爷收集的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182928</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188706</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>自从他被消防队长批评后，他就没有烧过任何东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188706</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192309</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好像有几只鸡一直把这里当成窝了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192309</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196676</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奥利维亚指着草堆上的六个褐色鸡蛋说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196676</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200558</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它们的颜色几乎和落叶一样。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200558</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205891</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇啊。” 乔伊说，“这就是最近鸡蛋很少的原因。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205891</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209432</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它们为什么那么做呢？” 凯蒂问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209432</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212498</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊耸了耸肩，“我也不知道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212498</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217896</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>也许它们出去只是想找个柔软的地方下蛋而已吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217896</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223262</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在我们只需要找到母鸡们......” 奥利维亚开始说话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223262</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225883</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道了！” 凯蒂喊道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225883</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230624</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们到树屋去吧。那里会很容易发现它们的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230624</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234909</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她们迅速爬上了树屋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234909</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242194</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“凯蒂，你真是个天才！我看见它们了！” 奥利维亚喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242194</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246257</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她指了指在小溪边的四只鸡。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246257</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253323</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“任务完成！” 乔伊说。她们把所有的鸡都找到了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253323</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259048</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“刚才我发现它们是怎么出去的了。” 凯蒂补充说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259048</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262392</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她把手伸进了栅栏之间的一个缺口，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262392</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265501</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个铁丝网已经不牢固了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265501</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270280</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我去问问妈妈我能不能用爸爸的工具。” 乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270280</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273973</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在爷爷回来以前，我要修好它！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273973</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278677</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“时间还来得及。” 奥利维亚说着抬头看了看，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278677</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282942</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>黑灰色的乌云正在从她们头上飘过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282942</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290093</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“暴风好像要来了，天气好冷，感觉要下雪了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>